Class Octahedron

  • java.lang.Object
    • Shapes
      • ThreeDimensionalShapes
        • AngleBase3DShapes
          • Octahedron

  • public class Octahedron
extends AngleBase3DShapes
    Version:
    1.0

    This is a subclass of AngleBase3DShapes. This class will create a Octahedron with all edges the same length.

    Author:
    Alex Wong wong4a@gmail.com
